com.adobe.cq.commerce.common

Class VendorJcrPlacedOrder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.adobe.cq.commerce.common.VendorJcrPlacedOrder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PlacedOrder

    public class VendorJcrPlacedOrder
extends java.lang.Object
implements PlacedOrder
    An editable implementation of a PlacedOrder, for use in order administration. NB: models vendor records in /var/commerce/orders/, not shopper records in ~/commerce/orders/. For (read-only) access to shopper records, see DefaultJcrPlacedOrder.

        public void updateOrder(java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.Object> delta,
                        boolean autoSave)
                 throws CommerceException
        Update a number of properties in the order record. Currently this is a "raw" update; there is no re-calculation involved.
        Parameters:
        delta - The properties to update. Properties not in this set will NOT be removed; to remove a property include it with a value of null.
        autoSave - If true, the current session will be saved after updating the order.
        Throws:
        CommerceException
